CodeClear.​NaturalDocs.​Engine.​Collections.​ILookupKey
public interface
CodeClear.​NaturalDocs.​Engine.​Collections.​ILookupKey
CodeClear.​NaturalDocs.​Engine.​Symbols.​ClassString
CodeClear.​NaturalDocs.​Engine.​Symbols.​ContextString

An interface for any class that needs to be indexed with a specific key that differs from what's returned by ToString().

For example, Symbols.ClassString's normal value is case sensitive but if its language is not it returns a lowercase string for the key instead.  It doesn't use the lowercase key as the normal value because it wants to preserve the case as entered for display.

Properties
LookupKey
string LookupKey { get }

Returns the key that should be used when finding entries in the cache.
